{"tid":805941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張藝興x Alan Walker MV曝光","createTime":"2018-09-04T09:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T11:14:05.000Z","uid":160973,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7aa233e3eb8c6c5fbe1c773995767632d75052","tid":805941,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"韓國男團EXO的中國籍成員張藝興（Lay），自從一五年獲SM特准在內地自設工作室後，發展愈戰愈勇，除了在內地綜藝節目《極限挑戰》中的演出贏盡觀眾歡心，最近參與黃渤自導自演的電影《一齣好戲》，獲舒淇推薦做主角外，票房更突破13億元大關。<br />\n<br />\nLay早前為Mc Jin（歐陽靖）作曲，更與俘虜年輕一代的電音天王Alan Walker合作，將去年推出的第二張個人專輯中的主打歌《SHEEP》，由Alan Walker重新加持，並填上新歌詞，推出《Sheep （Alan Walker Relift）》版本，MV透過韓國MBC FM4U《梁耀燮的夢想電台》率先公開，歌曲將Lay狂野帥氣一面表露無遺，而舞蹈藝員幪上一半面的造型，亦貫徹了Alan Walker的神秘作風。<br />\n<br />\nAlan Walker近年希望將電音帶到亞洲地區，亦曾跟BIGBANG的勝利合作，今年初他與Lay在北京開始交流，共同創作Relift的版本，8月初Alan Walker更邀請Lay一起出席全球十大音樂節之一的《Lollapalooza音樂節》表演，作為首位登上這個舞台的華人歌手Lay，自然備受矚目，適逢Michael Jackson　60 歲冥壽，美國769唱片公司召集多位頂級音樂人，攜手炮製一張致敬專輯，Lay、韓團NCT 127、 Jason DeruloAnt Clemons與Bong Bytheway獲邀參與新曲《Let&rsquo;s Shut up and Dance》，雖然Lay當日在EXO中不是最亮眼的成員，但憑着他的音樂造詣加實力，與及他「努力努力再努力」的座右銘幹出好成績，比起他的「兄弟們」已走得更遠了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Q2W9Bm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Q2W9Bm&d=4LxgvR7ehd5k%2F1H1t1yFw%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ddc81f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Q2W9Bm</a>"},{"pid":"c4ec35dba5d25dd5d22336d0c7d5502d9564606a","tid":805941,"uid":60052,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"大陸加泡菜真係冇得輸..."},{"pid":"973171a088c17bf71d4c8897de4e3e214cf78ee1","tid":805941,"uid":137694,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"反還反<br />\n佢真係好撚靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e70004a9ce9ee1d72a7b228301a4765c4f1874e","tid":805941,"uid":34071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"佢同隻蝗邊個乞人憎d永遠都會係個難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021c5d6f68299b148c3620a55eba59b61d3fc8e1","tid":805941,"uid":169468,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"大陸lay"},{"pid":"52056c4daf80205c327322fd3d5b50b8e24b1872","tid":805941,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"雖然Lay當日在<span style=\"color: red;\">EXO中不是最亮眼</span>的成員，但憑着他的<span style=\"color: red;\">音樂造詣</span>加實力，與及他「努力努力再努力」的座右銘幹出好成績，<span style=\"color: red;\">比起他的「兄弟們」已走得更遠了</span>。<br />\n<br />\n哈，提到EXO嘅兄弟們要引號，個記者肯撚定係興迷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b759acbfebf30ceb4ee1abf495cccd3751b16987","tid":805941,"uid":189336,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f745671a4a4e2c9e4a6b933bd001f8379ab2356f","tid":805941,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e70004a9ce9ee1d72a7b228301a4765c4f1874e","tid":805941,"uid":34071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"佢同隻蝗邊個乞人憎d永遠都會係個難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"點解要比？一樣咁乞人憎唔得咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c07be183e8c31a2bc8bb58cc91482c728fe8c17","tid":805941,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"同樣係EXO出嚟 點解同kris wu比可以爭咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}